New support group helps people live well with diabetes
A group aimed at connecting people in Tower Hamlets living with diabetes, plus
carers of people with diabetes, has been launched.
Local residents Laura Dickens (pictured left) and Lynda Stewart (pictured
right) are behind the formation of the group.
